Challenge 31: Meeting Rooms
What to do:
Given an array of meeting time intervals consisting of start and end times, determine if a person can attend all meetings without overlap.
Example Input:
intervals = [[0,30],[5,10],[15,20]]
Example Output:
False
Explanation:
Meetings [0,30] and [5,10] overlap, so it’s impossible to attend all meetings.
